      <title>埃利奥特据称已持有巴菲特青睐的住友商事“大量”股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，埃利奥特管理公司(Elliott Management Corp.)已持有住友商事株式会社(Sumitomo Corp.)的“大量”股份，住友商事株式会社是沃伦·巴菲特最喜欢的日本贸易公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，中金公司将削减投资银行家的基本薪酬 25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/cicc-to-cut-investment-bankers-base-pay-by-25-reuters-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，中国国际金融公司正在将境内投资银行家的基本工资削减多达 25%，以削减成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/cicc-to-cut-investment-bankers-base-pay-by-25-reuters-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:05:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国成都市放宽购房规定以重振销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/chinese-city-of-chengdu-relaxes-home-buying-rule-to-revive-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国西南部的主要城市成都取消了购房限制，与国内数十个城市一起试图重振房地产需求并促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/chinese-city-of-chengdu-relaxes-home-buying-rule-to-revive-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 08:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元观察人士问，随着货币贬值加速，日本将何去何从？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/usd-jpy-yen-watchers-ask-where-is-japan-intervention-as-currency-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元已大幅下跌，跌破了日本的红线，其跌幅让交易员询问当局何时可能开始购买日元以支撑日元——以及为什么他们还没有这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/usd-jpy-yen-watchers-ask-where-is-japan-intervention-as-currency-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在取消印度一周后，马斯克出人意料地访问中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)在推迟对印度的访问一周后，周日对中国进行了一次未经宣布的访问，以处理该汽车制造商的紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东南亚热浪导致学校停课，引发电力需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾宣布将停止公立学校的面授课程，而泰国的电力需求则升至创纪录水平，因为席卷南亚的热浪继续造成损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
